<lyrics>[V1]
 1- wʿdt ṭryqy trsẖdny .. tʿlmny wtnṣḥny
 wfy ạlbryẗ tsndny .. bạ̹ydk ạ̹nt tmskny
 ạlqrạr- wạ̉kyd ạlwʿd dạ lyã .. ḍmạnh fyk wmsẖ fyã
 klạm ṣạdq ạ̹lh ṣạlḥ .. ạ̉myn mạ ttgẖyr
 2- wʿdt wḍmnt ạ̹ḥsạnk .. wạnạ ṣgẖyr wlạ ạ̉stạhl
 wtgẖm qlby bslạmk .. wtḥfẓ fkry bạlkạml
 3- wʿdt ạ̹nk bslṭạnk .. lkẖyry ạlkl ytḥwl
 mạ kl sẖyʾ fy ạ̹mkạnk .. wmjdk ạ̹nt fy ạlạ̉wl
 4- wʿdt ạ̹nk htsẖfyny .. bklmẗ wlmsẗ ạ̹lhyẗ
 ạ̹lhy ạlḥy njyny .. dạ kl qdrtk lyã</lyrics>
<title>wʿdt ṭryqy trsẖdny</title>
